    "(B 2, G 0 /K 0)) with g B ∈ c and ρ(π 1 (B)) ≤ G 0.",
    "Then, the map HE 0 → HE is finite-to-one.Proof.",
    "Let (g B, ρ, h) be a solution to the twisted harmonic-Einstein equation with g B ∈ c and ρ(π1 (B)) ≤ G 0."
